nextMessages

public static play.libs.F.Promise<java.util.List<play.libs.F.IndexedEvent<UserEvent.Event>>> nextMessages(long lastReceived)
For long polling, as we are sometimes disconnected, we need to pass the last event seen id, to be sure to not miss any message. Gets the messages that have been published to the event stream for the chat room

Parameters:
lastReceived - the id of the last message the caller has seen. Messages with ids greater than lastReceived are returned
Returns:
list of messages with ids > lastReceived
